_sText:
Well this is my first map for Zombie Mod and the people in the [Fish]Zombie server seem to like it.

Next beta test I will put up the rest of the info, but here is the layout. Two sides that CT or T spawns on. CT spawns in the Cabin, T spawns outside near the gate or the guard building as I like to call it.

There are a few secret teleporters and there is a teleporter that traps glitchers in the fire room (aka the Jail). 

Also in one of the rooms there is a back door so look out if you choose to camp there.

I will add more info if necessary.

And on a side note -=ETO=- Caboose is my in game name.
